When using the Rich Text Editor (RTE) the markup will be broken if a panel macro, such as warning, tip or info, is immediately before a list or a table.

Steps to produce:
# Set RTE mode as default
# Go to wiki markup mode 
# Insert the command:
{noformat}
  {warning}This is buit in the RTE.{warning}
|| Name || Address \\ ||
| | |
{noformat}
# Save the changes
# Goto edit
 # Switch to wiki markup mode
# Save the changes

Results:

